gbrainy is a brain teaser game and trainer to have fun and to keep your brain
trained.

It provides the following types of games:

 - Logic puzzles. Games designed to challenge your reasoning and thinking
 - skills. Mental calculation. Games based on arithmetical operations
 - designed to prove your mental calculation skills. Memory trainers. Games
 - designed to challenge your short term memory. 

gbrainy provides enough flexibility in terms of number of games, difficulty
levels and parametrization to make it enjoyable for kids, adults or senior
citizens.

WWW:	http://live.gnome.org/gbrainy/
